items.title: Chicago Fed's Goolsbee says he's cautious about further rate cuts during shutdown

items.title: Private payrolls rose 42,000 in October, more than expected and countering labor market fears, ADP says
items.description: Companies added 42,000 jobs for the month, following a decline of 29,000 and topping the estimate for a gain of 22,000.
